00:04:40.604 --> 00:04:43.631
And so we were like perfectly positioned

101
00:04:43.631 --> 00:04:46.805
as a couple of other business schools were

102
00:04:46.805 --> 00:04:49.689
to jump on this bandwagon and say; okay

103
00:04:49.689 --> 00:04:53.020
this is Decision Sciences.

104
00:04:53.020 --> 00:04:55.935
And Foster Provost who's
in my department was

105
00:04:55.935 --> 00:05:00.102
the first director of the
NYU Center for Data Science.

